casebody.data:
Derrick Lamont TAYLOR
v.
HARNETT COUNTY SUPERIOR COURT, Jacqualyn L. Lee. No. 330P15. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Nov. 5, 2015. Derrick Lamont Taylor, for Taylor, Derrick Lamont. Robert C. Montgomery, Special Deputy Attorney General, for Harnett County Superior Court.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Plaintiff on the 23rd of September 2015 in this matter for a writ of mandamus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Harnett County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 5th of November 2015."
